WEBVTT

01:49.320 --> 01:52.120
I'll fight for what I want myself.

01:52.360 --> 01:53.720
I don't need you to go easy on me.

01:53.720 --> 01:55.600
What I want to do is my own freedom.

01:56.320 --> 01:58.050
You have no right to control me.

01:58.120 --> 01:59.320
The match hasn't started yet.

01:59.320 --> 02:00.880
Fine, Xiong Yuanbao.

02:01.040 --> 02:01.970
You've got guts.

02:02.080 --> 02:04.360
You'd better remember what you just said.

02:04.360 --> 02:06.320
Today, I will let you know

02:06.640 --> 02:08.919
what a crushing defeat is.

02:11.760 --> 02:12.620
Xiong Yuanbao.

02:25.600 --> 02:26.600
Xiong Yuanbao, what are you doing?

02:26.600 --> 02:27.920
Why did you throw water at me?

02:27.920 --> 02:29.480
Xiong Yuanbao, what are you doing?

02:29.480 --> 02:30.280
What's wrong?

02:30.480 --> 02:31.400
Xiong Yuanbao,

02:32.120 --> 02:33.440
If you don't want me to enter the competition, just say it.

02:33.440 --> 02:34.960
Why do you treat me like this?

02:34.960 --> 02:36.120
What kind of person are you?

02:36.120 --> 02:38.240
You use such despicable tricks when you can't beat us in dancing.

02:38.240 --> 02:39.320
Are you that afraid of us winning?

02:39.320 --> 02:41.160
You throw water because you can't beat us in cheerleading?

02:41.160 --> 02:41.960
What are you talking about?

02:41.960 --> 02:43.560
She must have bullied Yuanbao first.

02:43.560 --> 02:44.079
How is that possible?

02:44.079 --> 02:44.640
Exactly.

02:44.680 --> 02:46.240
If Gu Xinrui didn't bully her,

02:46.240 --> 02:48.079
why would Yuanbao throw water at you?

02:48.079 --> 02:50.079
She's already like this. How could she verbally abuse anyone?

02:50.079 --> 02:50.680
You guys are too much.

02:50.680 --> 02:51.600
Who bullied you?

02:51.600 --> 02:53.600
You're the one bullying us every time.

02:53.600 --> 02:54.960
You're the one bullying us every time.

02:54.960 --> 02:57.220
We're the ones tolerating it every time.

03:16.600 --> 03:17.600
Are we even?

03:18.520 --> 03:19.650
See you on the field.

04:05.440 --> 04:06.960
Wipe yourself with my clothes first.

04:06.960 --> 04:09.090
I'll go get a towel from Ruirui for you.

04:39.000 --> 04:39.720
Yuanbao,

04:40.120 --> 04:40.840
Yuanbao,

04:41.080 --> 04:41.840
are you okay?

04:42.520 --> 04:43.480
Are you okay?

04:43.520 --> 04:44.800
How did this happen?

04:45.480 --> 04:46.960
If I tell you

04:48.040 --> 04:49.440
that I didn't splash her,

04:49.880 --> 04:51.480
would you believe me?

04:51.680 --> 04:53.400
Of course we believe you.

04:55.240 --> 04:57.080
So she splashed

04:57.360 --> 04:59.080
water on herself.

05:01.280 --> 05:01.960
Qiao Yan.

05:03.080 --> 05:04.000
At that time,

05:05.000 --> 05:06.040
no one was there.

05:07.120 --> 05:09.680
They wouldn't believe you even if you told them.

05:09.680 --> 05:11.540
Are we just going to swallow this?

05:11.920 --> 05:14.840
Forget it. Our competition is coming up.

05:15.960 --> 05:17.360
Don't let them affect us.

05:20.760 --> 05:21.360
Okay.

05:21.760 --> 05:22.840
Let's fight them.

05:23.120 --> 05:25.440
Their cheerleading squad is very professional.

05:25.440 --> 05:26.360
You two shouldn't

05:26.360 --> 05:28.420
put too much pressure on yourselves.

05:28.440 --> 05:30.160
We just need to do our best.

05:30.160 --> 05:32.820
There's no need to force a comparison with them.

05:32.920 --> 05:34.520
The more she wants us to lose,

05:34.920 --> 05:36.320
the more we can't give up.

05:36.680 --> 05:38.210
Let's do our best together.

05:38.560 --> 05:39.120
Let's go.

05:39.280 --> 05:39.880
Let's go.

05:40.600 --> 05:41.440
Let's go.

05:43.440 --> 05:44.640
What happened to your hand?

05:44.640 --> 05:46.300
Why is there such a big bruise?

05:47.760 --> 05:48.560
It's nothing.

05:48.800 --> 05:50.600
I accidentally fell yesterday.

05:50.680 --> 05:51.280
It's fine.

05:51.400 --> 05:53.159
It's so purple. It must hurt a lot.

05:53.159 --> 05:54.680
It doesn't hurt. I'm fine.

05:55.560 --> 05:56.690
How did this happen?

05:56.760 --> 05:57.920
Did you apply any medicine?

05:57.920 --> 05:59.360
Let me take you to the infirmary.

05:59.360 --> 06:00.320
No need.

06:01.720 --> 06:02.840
I'm really fine.

06:03.680 --> 06:04.680
Qiao Yan.

06:06.040 --> 06:07.920
Is something going on with you?

06:08.800 --> 06:10.600
If you have any difficulties,

06:11.360 --> 06:12.400
just tell us.

06:12.680 --> 06:13.960
We will all help you.

06:16.520 --> 06:17.640
Are you two silly?

06:17.720 --> 06:19.250
What could be wrong with me?

06:19.880 --> 06:21.280
Alright, hurry up and go.

06:21.960 --> 06:22.800
Let's go.

06:22.880 --> 06:23.800
So silly.

06:24.640 --> 06:25.480
It's fine.

06:49.920 --> 06:50.720
Shang Ningyu,

06:51.360 --> 06:51.880
should I put it there?

06:51.880 --> 06:53.000
Yes, put it there.

07:08.640 --> 07:11.240
Who do you think will win between the two teams?

07:11.240 --> 07:13.770
Do you even have to ask? Definitely Gu Xinrui.

07:13.920 --> 07:15.320
I was on my way here just now

07:15.320 --> 07:16.960
and saw the costumes they changed into.

07:16.960 --> 07:18.220
They are super pretty.

07:18.680 --> 07:19.960
A couple of days ago on the field,

07:19.960 --> 07:21.880
I saw the dance Xiong Yuanbao's team was practicing.

07:21.880 --> 07:23.610
They all looked like gorillas.

07:23.720 --> 07:24.800
It was hilarious.

07:25.200 --> 07:26.440
I saw it too.

07:26.600 --> 07:28.480
The way they looked, oh my god.

07:29.960 --> 07:32.400
Look at Gu Xinrui, she didn't even take the field today,

07:32.400 --> 07:34.730
but she still got her team trained so well.

07:34.960 --> 07:36.400
We'll see the results in a bit.

07:36.400 --> 07:37.320
Come on, students.

07:37.320 --> 07:38.600
Come on, everyone have a seat.

07:38.600 --> 07:39.520
Listen up.

07:39.760 --> 07:41.720
The players for our class basketball game

07:41.720 --> 07:43.050
have all been selected.

07:43.480 --> 07:44.880
And the boys have been

07:45.040 --> 07:46.600
practicing really well lately.

07:46.600 --> 07:47.400
However,

07:47.680 --> 07:49.040
the girls' cheerleading squad for our class

07:49.040 --> 07:50.440
hasn't been decided yet.

07:50.600 --> 07:51.120
So,

07:51.200 --> 07:52.720
we will use this PE class

07:52.800 --> 07:54.240
to hold a mini-competition.

07:54.240 --> 07:55.680
One team led by Gu Xinrui,

07:56.159 --> 07:57.520
and the other by Xiong Yuanbao.

07:57.520 --> 07:58.760
We will vote

07:58.840 --> 08:00.480
to finally decide which team

08:00.520 --> 08:02.980
will perform at the school basketball game.

08:03.320 --> 08:05.120
Gu Xinrui, get ready to perform.

08:05.520 --> 08:06.480
Okay, Mr. Tian.

08:23.600 --> 08:25.330
Look at her outfit and her aura.

08:25.360 --> 08:26.480
Really good.

08:27.160 --> 08:29.680
Just the momentum of a simple entrance wins.

08:29.920 --> 08:31.320
Where is Xiong Yuanbao's team?

08:31.320 --> 08:33.049
Why hasn't any of them shown up?

08:33.240 --> 08:34.360
They must be too shabby,

08:34.360 --> 08:35.960
and too embarrassed to come.

08:36.120 --> 08:37.120
Maybe they will

08:37.120 --> 08:38.450
just give up in a moment.

09:38.560 --> 09:39.920
Very good. Very good.

09:40.000 --> 09:41.480
I didn't expect you

09:41.560 --> 09:43.000
to rehearse this so well in such a short time.

09:43.000 --> 09:44.360
If you perform at the basketball game,

09:44.360 --> 09:46.960
you will definitely be the biggest highlight.

09:47.000 --> 09:47.860
Wait, teacher.

09:47.960 --> 09:50.360
Yuanbao and the others haven't danced yet.

09:50.600 --> 09:51.480
Right.

09:52.760 --> 09:53.680
Where is Yuanbao?

09:53.680 --> 09:55.120
They are already here, Mr. Tian.

09:55.120 --> 09:56.000
I will go find them now.

09:56.000 --> 09:56.480
Okay.

10:10.640 --> 10:11.600
Okay, Gu Xinrui.

10:11.680 --> 10:12.940
You guys go take a rest.

10:17.960 --> 10:18.640
How was it?

10:18.840 --> 10:20.370
I told you I was bound to win.

10:28.720 --> 10:29.600
How is it, class monitor?

10:29.600 --> 10:31.000
Are Xiong Yuanbao and her team ready?

10:31.000 --> 10:32.400
They are ready, Mr. Tian.

10:32.520 --> 10:33.080
Good.

10:33.200 --> 10:34.400
Come on, get on stage.

11:43.440 --> 11:44.160
Yuanbao!

11:44.760 --> 11:45.640
You can do it!

12:45.480 --> 12:48.400
Everyone only sees her glamorous side,

12:49.160 --> 12:51.890
but they don't know the sweat and tears behind it.

12:52.840 --> 12:54.770
Yuanbao deserves all this praise.

12:55.680 --> 12:58.560
In the future, she will definitely stand on a higher stage

12:58.560 --> 13:00.090
and receive more applause.

13:07.000 --> 13:07.480
Mutou.

13:09.680 --> 13:11.940
You think you can buy me with an ice cream?

13:12.080 --> 13:13.040
Of course not.

13:13.280 --> 13:15.640
Don't worry. I'll treat you to a meal this weekend.

13:15.640 --> 13:17.080
Order whatever you want. Eat as much as you can.

13:17.080 --> 13:18.010
Don't hold back.

13:20.400 --> 13:21.160
Mutou,

13:22.160 --> 13:22.960
thank you.

13:23.520 --> 13:24.960
What are you thanking me for this time?

13:24.960 --> 13:25.960
What do you think?

13:26.160 --> 13:28.520
Slowly. Slower.

13:29.200 --> 13:30.800
Come on.

13:31.440 --> 13:32.800
Three, two, one.

13:33.120 --> 13:34.280
Surprise!

13:37.600 --> 13:38.880
Is this...

13:39.200 --> 13:40.130
A friend of mine,

13:40.240 --> 13:42.040
his aunt is a dance teacher here.

13:42.080 --> 13:44.320
She said we can use it for free for a few days.

13:44.320 --> 13:45.200
Really?

13:45.480 --> 13:47.340
Oh my god. Mutou, you're the best.

13:47.480 --> 13:50.040
Now we don't have to train on the playground,

13:50.440 --> 13:52.040
and people won't laugh at us.

13:52.760 --> 13:54.640
Come on. I'll take you to a good place.

13:54.640 --> 13:55.320
Where?

13:55.480 --> 13:56.520
Just follow me.

13:58.600 --> 13:59.560
Two, three, four.

13:59.560 --> 14:00.800
Two, three, four.

14:01.160 --> 14:04.480
Five, six, seven, eight.

14:04.920 --> 14:07.680
Two, two, three, four.

14:08.360 --> 14:10.040
How is it? Any inspiration?

14:11.120 --> 14:12.880
If our performance

14:13.280 --> 14:15.280
also uses this dance style,

14:15.680 --> 14:16.680
what do you think?

14:16.680 --> 14:19.040
Not bad. You're getting the hang of it.

14:19.440 --> 14:20.240
That's it.

14:20.520 --> 14:22.000
Professionally speaking,

14:22.000 --> 14:24.240
we can't beat that Gu Xinrui.

14:24.280 --> 14:26.720
But we can take a different approach.

14:26.920 --> 14:28.650
Surprise is the key to winning.

14:29.760 --> 14:30.400
Exactly.

14:31.000 --> 14:31.560
Right?

14:34.400 --> 14:35.560
Without you,

14:35.680 --> 14:37.600
we wouldn't have won this competition.

14:37.600 --> 14:39.260
Half of the credit goes to you.

14:40.760 --> 14:43.600
Don't be obsessed with me. I'm just a legend.

14:55.600 --> 14:56.840
We can rent this classroom

14:56.840 --> 14:58.440
to you by the hour.

14:58.520 --> 14:59.200
Since you're a student

14:59.200 --> 15:00.880
and have been here so many times,

15:00.880 --> 15:02.680
I'll charge you 20 yuan an hour.

15:02.760 --> 15:03.720
Think about it.

15:04.000 --> 15:05.160
If you want to rent it...

15:05.160 --> 15:06.680
Thank you. I'll rent it.

15:06.840 --> 15:08.000
I'd like to use it today.

15:08.000 --> 15:09.000
Okay, sure.

15:09.080 --> 15:11.280
Then come with me to pay the rent.

15:19.880 --> 15:20.880
Family.

15:42.520 --> 15:43.850
What are you looking at?

15:45.680 --> 15:46.680
Nothing. I'm not looking at anything.

15:46.680 --> 15:49.280
I was just seeing how far you've written.

16:01.560 --> 16:02.820
What's wrong with you?

16:02.920 --> 16:05.050
Why do you keep looking at me like that?

16:06.600 --> 16:08.320
Well, next week, my buddies and I

16:08.320 --> 16:09.920
are going to pull an all-nighter at the internet cafe.

16:09.920 --> 16:12.380
Should I log into your chat app to level it up?

16:12.880 --> 16:13.680
Really?

16:14.640 --> 16:15.440
That's great!

16:16.200 --> 16:18.460
I only have two moons and a star right now.

16:18.640 --> 16:20.520
Brother Qingjun already has three suns.

16:20.520 --> 16:22.160
Even Yuanbao has a sun.

16:22.360 --> 16:23.040
Don't worry.

16:23.040 --> 16:25.120
As long as I go in the future, I'll log in for you.

16:25.120 --> 16:28.040
I promise your level will shoot right up.

16:29.320 --> 16:30.160
Thank you.

16:32.640 --> 16:33.280
Oh, right.

16:33.520 --> 16:35.520
Could you find some time

16:35.760 --> 16:37.890
to decorate my chat app profile for me?

16:38.040 --> 16:40.000
A new skin just came out

16:40.120 --> 16:41.280
called 'Winter Sonata'.

16:41.280 --> 16:42.480
It looks really nice.

16:44.240 --> 16:45.840
My mom is very strict with me.

16:45.920 --> 16:47.650
I can't go to the internet cafe.

16:49.400 --> 16:50.000
Also,

16:50.480 --> 16:51.440
could you check

16:51.560 --> 16:53.400
if anyone visited my profile

16:54.120 --> 16:55.800
or left me any messages?

16:56.520 --> 16:57.240
No problem.

16:58.360 --> 16:59.480
Thanks.

17:01.760 --> 17:02.960
Don't mention it.

17:03.560 --> 17:04.760
We're not strangers.

17:08.040 --> 17:08.720
I mean,

17:09.240 --> 17:10.400
we're good friends,

17:10.440 --> 17:11.839
and good classmates.

17:13.000 --> 17:14.119
It's fine.

17:15.680 --> 17:16.440
Thanks.

17:16.640 --> 17:18.720
No talking. Focus on your homework.

17:30.120 --> 17:31.960
Well? Have you made up your mind?

17:35.720 --> 17:36.640
Class,

17:37.520 --> 17:39.650
after the selection within our class,

17:40.320 --> 17:41.920
congratulations to Xiong Yuanbao's cheerleading squad

17:41.920 --> 17:43.450
for winning by a landslide.

17:49.360 --> 17:50.080
Similarly,

17:50.680 --> 17:51.800
Gu Xinrui's team

17:51.960 --> 17:53.000
was also excellent.

17:53.000 --> 17:54.360
If there's a chance in the future,

17:54.360 --> 17:55.640
we'll take turns.

17:56.080 --> 17:58.280
Let's give them a round of applause too.

17:59.480 --> 18:00.720
I'll say it again.

18:01.000 --> 18:02.520
It's the taking part that counts.

18:02.520 --> 18:05.160
Next up is the autumn sports meet.

18:05.360 --> 18:07.020
And then the basketball game.

18:07.120 --> 18:09.180
I took a look at our class's PE grades.

18:09.440 --> 18:10.640
They are all average.

18:11.040 --> 18:12.200
Although Gong Yu

18:12.280 --> 18:13.410
is a sports student,

18:13.600 --> 18:15.960
he can't participate due to his injury.

18:16.160 --> 18:17.120
So when the time comes,

18:17.120 --> 18:18.160
our class

18:18.360 --> 18:20.120
must give the participating students

18:20.120 --> 18:21.480
the warmest applause.

18:21.720 --> 18:22.920
In terms of momentum,

18:22.920 --> 18:24.160
we definitely can't lose to other classes.

18:24.160 --> 18:24.760
All right?

18:24.840 --> 18:25.600
Yes.

18:29.640 --> 18:31.120
I am a sports student,

18:31.200 --> 18:33.600
but I can't participate in the sports meet.

18:33.760 --> 18:34.640
So funny.

18:36.040 --> 18:38.160
Bro, don't be discouraged.

18:38.640 --> 18:39.770
When you are healed,

18:39.840 --> 18:41.120
there will be chances.

18:59.160 --> 19:00.720
Look who it is.

19:32.600 --> 19:33.680
Come on!

19:33.760 --> 19:35.560
Come on, Gong Yu!

19:35.720 --> 19:37.400
Come on, Gong Yu!

20:13.520 --> 20:14.240
Gong Yu!

20:14.600 --> 20:16.120
Gong Yu's leg is injured,

20:16.680 --> 20:18.810
so he is not qualified to participate.

20:18.920 --> 20:20.520
Even if he stands outside the track,

20:20.520 --> 20:22.380
he still wants to finish the race.

20:22.640 --> 20:23.440
Maybe

20:23.920 --> 20:25.480
this is the real Gong Yu.

20:26.360 --> 20:28.560
We didn't know him well enough before.

20:36.000 --> 20:37.840
Grandma, actually last time,

20:37.960 --> 20:39.640
Gong Yu and I planned

20:39.680 --> 20:41.680
to let you and his grandpa meet

20:41.720 --> 20:42.520
and chat.

20:43.080 --> 20:44.280
But we messed up.

20:44.720 --> 20:47.000
We know you knew each other when you were young.

20:47.000 --> 20:48.000
So,

20:48.480 --> 20:49.800
Grandpa Gong is a really nice person.

20:49.800 --> 20:51.660
Meet him again when you have time.

20:52.840 --> 20:54.040
I am getting old

20:54.320 --> 20:56.120
and don't want to think too much.

20:56.640 --> 20:58.040
All I want now is

20:58.440 --> 21:01.040
for Yuanbao and you to have a good future.

21:01.680 --> 21:03.440
To have a stable job

21:03.760 --> 21:05.480
and a happy family.

21:06.120 --> 21:07.650
That would be enough for me.

21:08.040 --> 21:10.440
Grandma, I know what you're worried about.

21:11.360 --> 21:14.200
Aren't you just worried about what Yuanbao thinks?

21:14.200 --> 21:14.930
Don't worry.

21:15.240 --> 21:16.600
I will talk to her.

21:17.600 --> 21:18.360
Mutou.

21:21.280 --> 21:22.240
Come out with me for a second.

21:22.240 --> 21:23.900
I have something to say to you.

21:29.120 --> 21:30.680
I'll go first, Grandma.

21:37.200 --> 21:38.960
Yuanbao, listen to me.

21:39.040 --> 21:39.760
Say what?

21:40.040 --> 21:42.600
That everything you did is for my own good,

21:42.800 --> 21:44.280
and for Grandma's own good?

21:44.280 --> 21:46.680
Who else would I be doing this for if not you?

21:46.800 --> 21:47.680
Mu Qingyun,

21:48.320 --> 21:50.720
what gives you the right to do this behind my back,

21:50.720 --> 21:53.080
and introduce a partner to my grandma?

21:55.000 --> 21:56.600
Didn't you disagree before?

21:57.040 --> 21:59.120
I thought I'd ask Grandma first.

21:59.280 --> 22:00.920
If she's okay with it,

22:01.040 --> 22:02.360
then I'd discuss it with you.

22:02.360 --> 22:03.160
Mu Qingyun,

22:03.800 --> 22:04.800
can you stay out of

22:04.880 --> 22:06.140
our family's affairs?

22:07.120 --> 22:09.080
Your family's affairs?

22:11.320 --> 22:12.120
That's right.

22:12.640 --> 22:15.240
You'd better stay out of our family's affairs.

22:18.640 --> 22:21.170
Xiong Yuanbao, can you stop being so selfish?

22:24.840 --> 22:25.440
I know you're not ready

22:25.440 --> 22:26.480
for this.

22:27.600 --> 22:29.400
But can you think about Grandma?

22:29.560 --> 22:30.240
Gong Yu's grandfather also

22:30.240 --> 22:31.760
raised him all by himself.

22:32.200 --> 22:33.040
How could he think of

22:33.040 --> 22:35.240
finding a partner for his grandfather?

22:35.760 --> 22:36.360
Yuanbao,

22:36.840 --> 22:38.080
I know you feel bad.

22:38.880 --> 22:40.740
I also know what you're thinking.

22:41.120 --> 22:42.380
You only have Grandma.

22:42.680 --> 22:44.140
You don't want to lose her,

22:44.200 --> 22:46.000
let alone share her with anyone.

22:55.600 --> 22:56.320
But...

22:57.640 --> 23:00.720
It wasn't easy for Grandma to raise you.

23:01.400 --> 23:02.920
Her world can't just revolve around you.

23:02.920 --> 23:03.600
Right?

23:04.960 --> 23:05.820
Think about it.

23:06.360 --> 23:08.160
We're going to college soon.

23:08.440 --> 23:09.960
Are you going to leave her

23:10.080 --> 23:11.120
all alone?

23:24.880 --> 23:26.160
Grandma, I'm not eating.

23:26.160 --> 23:27.240
I'm going to be late.

23:27.240 --> 23:28.400
How can you not eat?

23:28.480 --> 23:29.410
Here, take this.

23:29.480 --> 23:30.440
Eat it at school.

23:31.160 --> 23:31.920
Got it.

23:38.760 --> 23:39.480
Grandma!

23:44.400 --> 23:45.160
Grandma!

23:45.600 --> 23:46.360
Grandma!

23:47.240 --> 23:48.000
Grandma!

23:49.160 --> 23:51.080
Doctor, how is she?

23:51.960 --> 23:53.440
Her blood pressure was just measured.

23:53.440 --> 23:55.640
Systolic 180, diastolic 120.

23:56.240 --> 23:58.640
The dizziness is still caused by high blood pressure.

23:58.640 --> 24:00.040
We'll give her an IV later

24:00.120 --> 24:01.720
to lower her blood pressure.

24:01.720 --> 24:04.040
Ma'am, you can't stop taking your blood pressure medication.

24:04.040 --> 24:05.700
Remember to take it every day.

24:06.640 --> 24:07.720
It's nothing serious.

24:07.720 --> 24:09.480
You don't need so many people to stay here.

24:09.480 --> 24:10.440
One is enough.

24:11.000 --> 24:12.520
Okay, thank you, doctor.

24:15.240 --> 24:16.240
I'm fine.

24:16.640 --> 24:17.720
Don't be afraid.

24:21.480 --> 24:22.960
I'll stay here to take care of Grandma.

24:22.960 --> 24:24.400
You two hurry to school.

24:25.080 --> 24:26.880
I'm not leaving. I want to stay.

24:27.760 --> 24:30.600
Be good. Your studies are important.

24:31.080 --> 24:33.000
Nothing is more important than you.

24:33.000 --> 24:34.560
Say no more. Get some sleep first.

24:34.560 --> 24:35.240
I will stay right here.

24:35.240 --> 24:36.570
I'm not going anywhere.

24:37.200 --> 24:38.480
I'm not going anywhere either.

24:38.480 --> 24:39.760
I will stay and keep you company.

24:39.760 --> 24:41.490
Why are you joining in the fuss?

24:41.880 --> 24:42.940
This is a hospital.

24:43.000 --> 24:44.400
If so many of us stay here,

24:44.440 --> 24:46.000
others won't be able to rest.

24:46.000 --> 24:47.880
Besides, it's not convenient for a boy like you.

24:47.880 --> 24:48.880
Hurry to school.

24:50.000 --> 24:52.160
Mutou, you go to class first.

24:52.800 --> 24:55.240
Don't worry. I'll stay here and keep Grandma company.

24:55.240 --> 24:56.240
Then, Grandma,

24:57.160 --> 24:58.890
I'll come see you after school.

24:59.280 --> 25:00.280
Take care.

25:00.840 --> 25:02.120
Be careful on the road.

25:02.840 --> 25:04.040
Don't worry about me.

25:05.160 --> 25:05.960
Yuanbao,

25:07.720 --> 25:08.720
I'm leaving then.

25:10.960 --> 25:12.020
I'll go see him off.

25:28.560 --> 25:30.160
Nothing is more important than you.

25:30.160 --> 25:31.490
I'll stay here with you.

25:31.600 --> 25:32.730
I won't go anywhere.

25:38.120 --> 25:40.320
Mom, Dad, rest in peace.

25:40.320 --> 25:42.360
I will take good care of Grandma.

25:59.000 --> 26:01.600
What could have happened to Yuanbao's family?

26:13.320 --> 26:14.080
Yuanbao.

26:15.760 --> 26:17.760
You haven't eaten anything all day.

26:17.840 --> 26:19.170
Go get something to eat.

26:19.240 --> 26:20.300
I'll be right here.

26:20.880 --> 26:22.920
I'm not hungry, Auntie.

26:23.560 --> 26:25.600
I'll stay here to take care of Grandma.

26:25.600 --> 26:27.000
You go back and rest.

26:28.200 --> 26:29.720
How can you not eat anything?

26:29.720 --> 26:31.050
Go get something to eat.

26:31.880 --> 26:34.280
School is almost over.

26:34.800 --> 26:36.260
Qingyun will be here soon.

26:36.360 --> 26:38.160
He can also help take care of her.

26:38.840 --> 26:41.770
Then I'll go back to get some toiletries for Grandma.

26:42.400 --> 26:43.400
I'll be back soon.

26:52.000 --> 26:53.260
Be careful on the road.

27:20.560 --> 27:21.480
Who are you?

27:21.600 --> 27:23.330
Have you heard of Brother Shui?

27:26.760 --> 27:27.400
Kid,

27:28.240 --> 27:30.240
leave your name if you have the guts.

27:42.040 --> 27:43.640
What exactly do you want?

27:57.600 --> 27:58.680
How is Grandma?

28:00.520 --> 28:02.320
The doctor came to check a few times.

28:02.320 --> 28:03.980
They said she is quite stable.

28:05.200 --> 28:06.200
Where is Yuanbao?

28:11.120 --> 28:12.440
It's been over an hour.

28:12.800 --> 28:15.880
She said she was going home to get some toiletries for Grandma.

28:15.880 --> 28:17.480
Why hasn't she returned yet?

28:18.320 --> 28:20.840
This child hasn't eaten anything all day.

28:21.320 --> 28:23.120
You'd better go back and check on her.

28:23.120 --> 28:24.880
In case something happens to her on the road,

28:24.880 --> 28:26.410
or she faints or something.

28:27.920 --> 28:28.680
Slow down.

28:32.680 --> 28:33.320
Yuanbao!

28:34.640 --> 28:35.320
Yuanbao!

28:36.800 --> 28:37.440
Yuanbao!

28:45.480 --> 28:46.120
Yuanbao!

28:57.840 --> 28:59.040
She didn't come back.

29:05.440 --> 29:06.000
Ruirui.

29:11.720 --> 29:13.040
Shui.

29:13.320 --> 29:14.560
Didn't we say we'd just scare

29:14.560 --> 29:15.720
and warn her?

29:16.120 --> 29:17.520
If we don't let her go now,

29:17.560 --> 29:18.720
will we get into trouble?

29:18.720 --> 29:19.920
What? Are you scared?

29:20.480 --> 29:23.160
If it were anyone else, a few threats would be enough.

29:23.160 --> 29:25.840
But she happens to be the childhood friend Mu Qingyun cares about.

29:25.840 --> 29:26.520
That punk

29:26.840 --> 29:28.720
made me leave Yuhong in disgrace.

29:29.520 --> 29:30.840
Even now, Niu Ben and his gang

29:30.840 --> 29:32.200
are still laughing at me behind my back.

29:32.200 --> 29:34.520
I was worried I wouldn't get a chance to get revenge.

29:34.520 --> 29:36.720
Finally, such an opportunity has come.

29:36.840 --> 29:37.440
He and I

29:37.800 --> 29:39.000
need to settle this score.

29:39.000 --> 29:41.280
Th-Then what if he calls the police?

29:41.480 --> 29:44.680
What are you panicking for? It's only been a little while.

29:46.640 --> 29:47.440
Little girl,

29:48.000 --> 29:48.800
stop shaking.

29:49.840 --> 29:51.440
Of all the people you could hang out with,

29:51.440 --> 29:53.240
you just had to be Mu Qingyun's sister.

29:53.240 --> 29:54.080
Now look,

29:54.360 --> 29:56.360
you've dragged yourself into this.

29:56.800 --> 29:58.680
You don't need to look at me like that.

29:58.680 --> 30:00.480
I'm just doing a job for someone.

30:00.520 --> 30:01.280
Don't worry,

30:01.440 --> 30:02.960
I'm just giving you a warning.

30:02.960 --> 30:04.080
As long as you behave,

30:04.080 --> 30:05.360
I won't make things hard for you.

30:05.360 --> 30:06.320
But now,

30:07.680 --> 30:09.810
you need to call Mu Qingyun here for me.

30:14.760 --> 30:15.720
Is Yuanbao with you?

30:15.720 --> 30:16.640
Yuanbao?

30:17.320 --> 30:18.840
Didn't you say you had a family emergency

30:18.840 --> 30:19.880
and took the day off today?

30:19.880 --> 30:20.760
Okay, got it.

30:21.520 --> 30:22.200
Yuanbao.

30:27.840 --> 30:28.970
Is Yuanbao with you?

30:29.480 --> 30:30.740
She didn't contact me.

30:31.680 --> 30:33.080
I haven't seen her today.

30:33.200 --> 30:35.260
What's wrong? Did something happen?

30:36.600 --> 30:37.730
Where have you been?

30:42.120 --> 30:42.720
Xinrui.

30:42.840 --> 30:45.320
Come, taste how the chicken soup is.

30:48.400 --> 30:49.120
Xinrui.

30:50.040 --> 30:51.320
Come, have a taste.

30:51.520 --> 30:52.080
Okay.

30:53.160 --> 30:54.080
Did you get burned?

30:54.080 --> 30:54.480
It's fine.

30:54.480 --> 30:54.920
Did you get burned?

30:54.920 --> 30:55.450
I'm fine.

30:55.560 --> 30:57.240
Jingu, what are you spacing out for?

30:57.240 --> 30:58.570
Hurry up and get a towel.

30:59.320 --> 31:00.050
Are you okay?

31:00.360 --> 31:01.800
It's fine, Auntie.

31:02.680 --> 31:03.400
Xinrui,

31:04.360 --> 31:06.640
has something been on your mind recently?

31:06.640 --> 31:07.770
Did Jingu bully you?

31:08.280 --> 31:09.040
No, no.

31:09.160 --> 31:12.680
Uncle, I'm just feeling a bit stressed with my studies.

31:13.160 --> 31:16.020
After all, I've fallen too far behind in my classes.

31:16.480 --> 31:17.760
Your health is important.

31:17.760 --> 31:19.420
Don't just focus on studying.

31:19.480 --> 31:22.080
Have Jingu take you out for a walk this weekend.

31:22.240 --> 31:24.240
Don't always stay cooped up at home.

31:25.000 --> 31:26.400
Got it. Thank you, Uncle.

31:27.400 --> 31:29.320
I'm full. I'm going to study.

31:55.200 --> 31:56.960
Xiong Yuanbao, where are you?

31:57.080 --> 31:59.610
Aren't you too old to pull a disappearing act?

32:02.120 --> 32:03.000
Where is she?
